<h2>Your auction has ended</h2>

<p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

<p>Your auction <strong>{{auctionTitle}}</strong> has just ended.</p>

<table style='width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;'>
  <tr>
    <td style='padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background: #f9f9f9; font-weight: bold;'>Final price</td>
    <td style='padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;'><strong>{{finalPrice}}</strong></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style='padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; background: #f9f9f9; font-weight: bold;'>Winner</td>
    <td style='padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;'>
      {{#if hasWinner}}
        {{winnerName}}
      {{else}}
        No bids were placed
      {{/if}}
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p>View the auction details by clicking the link below:</p>

<p class='link-text'>{{auctionUrl}}</p>

<div class='divider'></div>

<p style='color: #999999; font-size: 14px;'>
  If you have any questions, please contact us through our website:
  <a href='{{appUrl}}/contact' style='color: #667eea;'>{{appName}}</a>.
</p>